						<div class="body-text body-text--pub">
							<body  ><div class="section"><p class="IndentMarginalone">The question was put that the<em> </em>amendments recommended by the Commerce Committee by majority be agreed to.</p><p class="VoteReason">A party vote was called for on the question,<em> </em><em>That the </em><em>question</em><em> be</em><em> </em><em>agreed to</em>.</p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Ayes 106</strong></p><p class="VoteText">New Zealand National 59; New Zealand Labour 31; Green Party 14; ACT New Zealand 1; United Future 1.</p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Noes 14</strong></p><p class="VoteText">New Zealand First 12; Māori Party 2.</p><p class="VoteResult">Question agreed to.</p><p class="IndentMarginalone">Bill read a second time.</p></div></body>
